:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(data=exam_data,
       aes(x= MATHS,
           y=ENGLISH)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method=lm,
              linewidth=0.5)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](HO_Ex1_submission_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-24-1.png){width=672}
